  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA 45">
<l>purintu matavēḻa māppiṭiyō ṭūṭit</l>
<l>tirintu ciṉattāṟ porutu – virintacīr</l>
<l>veṇkōṭṭu muttutirkkum vēṅkaṭamē mēlorunāṇ</l>
<l>maṇkōṭṭuk koṇṭāṉ malai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Vēṅkaṭam,</l>
<l>where the rutting bull elephant out of desire sulks with [his] dark cow,</l>
<l>runs about, fights out of anger [and] drops pearls from [his] wide, excellent</l>
<l>	white tusks , is the mountain of him</l>
<l>who on an earlier day took the earth on [his] tusk.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
